
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ระบบรับสมัครนักเรียน - โรงเรียนอรพิมพ์วิทยา</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sarabun:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Noto+Serif+Thai:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --navy: #0a2463;
            --navy-mid: #1a3a7a;
            --navy-light: #2c5fa8;
            --gold: #c8973a;
            --gold-light: #e8b95a;
            --gold-pale: #faf3e4;
            --cream: #fdfaf4;
            --text-dark: #1a1a2e;
            --text-mid: #4a4a6a;
            --text-light: #8888aa;
            --green: #1a6b4a;
            --green-mid: #22855c;
            --divider: rgba(10,36,99,0.12);
        }

        *, *::before, *::after {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Sarabun', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--cream);
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            background-image:
                radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 50% -10%, rgba(10,36,99,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%),
                repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent, transparent 79px, rgba(10,36,99,0.03) 79px, rgba(10,36,99,0.03) 80px),
                repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, transparent 79px, rgba(10,36,99,0.03) 79px, rgba(10,36,99,0.03) 80px);
        }

        /* ── Header Banner ── */
        .header-banner {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, var(--navy-mid) 60%, var(--navy-light) 100%);
            padding: 0;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header-banner::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%23ffffff' fill-opacity='0.03'%3E%3Cpath d='M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
        }

        .header-inner {
            max-width: 860px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 36px 24px 32px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 28px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .logo-frame {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            width: 96px;
            height: 96px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border: 2.5px solid var(--gold-light);
            padding: 4px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
        }

        .logo-frame img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            display: block;
        }

        .header-text { color: #fff; }

        .school-name {
            font-family: 'Noto Serif Thai', serif;
            font-size: 1.55rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.01em;
            line-height: 1.3;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .school-sub {
            font-size: 0.88rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
            font-weight: 300;
            letter-spacing: 0.02em;
        }

        /* gold divider line */
        .gold-rule {
            width: 100%;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold) 0%, var(--gold-light) 50%, transparent 100%);
        }

        /* ── Page title strip ── */
        .page-title-strip {
            background: #fff;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--divider);
            padding: 18px 24px;
        }

        .page-title-inner {
            max-width: 860px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .badge-year {
            background: var(--gold-pale);
            border: 1px solid var(--gold);
            color: var(--gold);
            font-size: 0.72rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 3px 10px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .page-title-text {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--navy);
        }

        /* ── Main content ── */
        .main {
            max-width: 860px;
            margin: 36px auto 60px;
            padding: 0 24px;
        }

        /* ── Section label ── */
        .section-label {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin: 0 0 16px;
        }

        .section-label-line {
            flex: 1;
            height: 1px;
            background: var(--divider);
        }

        .section-label-text {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            color: var(--text-light);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        /* ── Cards ── */
        .card-grid {
            display: grid;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .card-grid.cols-1 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .card-grid.cols-3 { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }

        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .card-grid.cols-3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }

        .card {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid var(--divider);
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 20px;
            padding: 22px 24px;
            transition: box-shadow 0.22s ease, transform 0.22s ease, border-color 0.22s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .card::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0;
            width: 4px;
        }

        .card.green::after  { background: var(--green); }
        .card.navy::after   { background: var(--navy); }

        .card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(10,36,99,0.1);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            border-color: rgba(10,36,99,0.2);
        }

        .card-icon {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .card.green .card-icon { background: rgba(26,107,74,0.08); }
        .card.navy  .card-icon { background: rgba(10,36,99,0.07); }

        .card-icon svg {
            width: 22px;
            height: 22px;
        }

        .card.green .card-icon svg { color: var(--green-mid); }
        .card.navy  .card-icon svg { color: var(--navy-light); }

        .card-body { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }

        .card-title {
            font-family: 'Noto Serif Thai', serif;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            margin-bottom: 3px;
        }

        .card-desc {
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            color: var(--text-light);
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .card-arrow {
            width: 28px;
            height: 28px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 1px solid var(--divider);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            transition: background 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
        }

        .card:hover .card-arrow {
            background: var(--navy);
            border-color: var(--navy);
        }

        .card:hover .card-arrow svg { color: #fff; }

        .card-arrow svg {
            width: 13px;
            height: 13px;
            color: var(--text-light);
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }

        /* ── Notice box ── */
        .notice {
            background: rgba(200,151,58,0.06);
            border: 1px solid rgba(200,151,58,0.3);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 14px 18px;
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .notice-icon {
            color: var(--gold);
            flex-shrink: 0;
            margin-top: 1px;
        }

        .notice-text {
            font-size: 0.84rem;
            color: var(--text-mid);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .notice-text strong {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--gold);
        }

        /* ── Spacer ── */
        .section-gap { margin-top: 32px; }

        /* ── Footer ── */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 28px 24px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--divider);
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .footer-logo-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .footer-logo-row img {
            width: 28px;
            height: 28px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }

        .footer-school-name {
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--navy);
        }

        .footer-address {
            font-size: 0.76rem;
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        /* ── Animate in ── */
        @keyframes fadeUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }
            to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .header-inner   { animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease both; }
        .page-title-inner { animation: fadeUp 0.5s 0.1s ease both; }
        .notice         { animation: fadeUp 0.5s 0.15s ease both; }
        .card-grid.cols-1 .card { animation: fadeUp 0.5s 0.2s ease both; }
        .card-grid.cols-3 .card:nth-child(1) { animation: fadeUp 0.5s 0.25s ease both; }
        .card-grid.cols-3 .card:nth-child(2) { animation: fadeUp 0.5s 0.32s ease both; }
        .card-grid.cols-3 .card:nth-child(3) { animation: fadeUp 0.5s 0.39s ease both; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ════════════ HEADER ════════════ -->
<div class="header-banner">
    <div class="header-inner">
        <div class="logo-frame">
            <img src="/img/logo.jpg"
                 alt="โลโก้โรงเรียนอรพิมพ์วิทยา">
        </div>
        <div class="header-text">
            <div class="school-name">โรงเรียนอรพิมพ์วิทยา</div>
            <div class="school-sub">ตำบลอรพิมพ์ อำเภอครบุรี จังหวัดนครราชสีมา</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="gold-rule"></div>
</div>

<!-- ════════════ PAGE TITLE STRIP ════════════ -->
<div class="page-title-strip">
    <div class="page-title-inner">
        <span class="badge-year">ปีการศึกษา 2569</span>
        <span class="page-title-text">ระบบรับสมัครนักเรียนออนไลน์</span>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- ════════════ MAIN CONTENT ════════════ -->
<main class="main">

    <!-- Notice -->
    <div class="notice">
        <svg class="notice-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="notice-text">
            <strong>แจ้งเพื่อทราบ:</strong> กรุณาเลือกระดับชั้นและแผนการเรียนที่ต้องการสมัคร แล้วกรอกข้อมูลให้ครบถ้วนและถูกต้อง เพื่อความสะดวกในการดำเนินการต่อไป
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ม.1 -->
    <div class="section-label">
        <span class="section-label-text">ระดับชั้นมัธยมศึกษาตอนต้น</span>
        <div class="section-label-line"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="card-grid cols-1">
        <a href="/form1" class="card green">
            <div class="card-icon">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="M22 10v6M2 10l10-5 10 5-10 5z"/><path d="M6 12v5c3 3 9 3 12 0v-5"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card-title">มัธยมศึกษาปีที่ 1 (ม.1)</div>
                <div class="card-desc">รับสมัครนักเรียนที่จบการศึกษาระดับประถมศึกษาปีที่ 6</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-arrow">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
        </a>
    </div>

    <!-- ม.4 -->
    <div class="section-gap"></div>
    <div class="section-label">
        <span class="section-label-text">ระดับชั้นมัธยมศึกษาตอนปลาย</span>
        <div class="section-label-line"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="card-grid cols-3">

        <a href="/form41" class="card navy">
            <div class="card-icon">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="M9 3H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4m6-6h10a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v4M9 3v18m0 0h10a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-4M9 21H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4m0 0h18"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card-title">วิทยาศาสตร์-คณิตศาสตร์</div>
                <div class="card-desc">แผนวิทยาศาสตร์ - คณิตศาสตร์</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-arrow">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/form42" class="card navy">
            <div class="card-icon">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card-title">คณิต - วิทย์ฯเเละเทคโนโลยี</div>
                <div class="card-desc">แผนเทคโนโลยีและนวัตกรรม</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-arrow">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/form43" class="card navy">
            <div class="card-icon">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card-title">ช่างทั่วไป</div>
                <div class="card-desc">แผนสายทักษะวิชาชีพ</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-arrow">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
        </a>

    </div>

</main>

<!-- ════════════ FOOTER ════════════ -->
<footer>
    <div class="footer-logo-row">
        <img src="https://scontent.fnak3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t39.30808-6/273132612_251595167153102_7617235967746055250_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=53a332&_nc_eui2=AeE7m3_1sEqqV2QGAklVQu3drKDYRiOogTWsoNhGI6iBNc1utvRSKRPIYWMxBB4HVizAQLH86yJYZxZlr-QgFyug&_nc_ohc=6W3ur_RsIs0Q7kNvwEIXfFL&_nc_oc=AdnquH93U0B2VIOYUJkiRVqMRqMv2kaUMOPlvW4JlVoNGcPWQYWY86__CDzPj6aX8zPb_N1vAGYQtwnHM2h42YTH&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.fnak3-1.fna&_nc_gid=Rcc8OJ9Vpkumcvy0BoBNSQ&_nc_ss=8&oh=00_AfyV1-Cm-zxxx0Tc4RJn4zBQT2CGBEUmpFSI3mdwEXdyIA&oe=69BA0471" alt="">
        <span class="footer-school-name">โรงเรียนอรพิมพ์วิทยา</span>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-address">ตำบลอรพิมพ์ อำเภอครบุรี จังหวัดนครราชสีมา &nbsp;|&nbsp; &copy; 2569</div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
